{"tid":1399813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 星晨旅遊 內部受到國內壓力 星期一照常營業","createTime":"2019-08-03T09:57:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T17:14:23.000Z","uid":28320,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bca7d8070ef76667e4cd9e1c312d4373986bf39d","tid":1399813,"uid":28320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:57:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">朋友內部得知消息</span><br />\n<br />\n咁多位可以有禮貌地<br />\n打電話/親身到分行<br />\n查詢星期一是否休息<br />\n要明確確實答覆<br />\n如果答唔實 就姐係想彈弓手<br />\n欺騙市民 呃完LIKE 就開工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hm5Dc73.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHm5Dc73.png&h=82c582ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果你地想幫一間良心公司<br />\n擺開共產黨嘅壓力<br />\n我地可以比返壓力佢地<br />\n令到佢地唔開工</span>"},{"pid":"cf007ddbebd8f80320acb4b89430a4e4043428f6","tid":1399813,"uid":28320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:59:44.000Z","msg":"香港人加油"},{"pid":"e32cd4f6073df24b07c7173d414ee5a5d1dcc05b","tid":1399813,"uid":224066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T10:03:52.000Z","msg":"四大蟈有銀行都話要擺工喎<br />\n五毛吧點解唔做埋佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fff7a0af4e582034d06aaa3f42b5dc21a7f0ea1","tid":1399813,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T10:04:57.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"aeadc34121a44627ae6a0ca8256cabef4da947a5","tid":1399813,"uid":21002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T10:21:44.000Z","msg":"朋友 消息人士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d915630080afd854e9a28adc631d444d61ed326","tid":1399813,"uid":28320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:14:23.000Z","msg":"推"}]}